/// | [032..036) | origin      | uint32  | 4     | Domain where Origin is located |
/// | [036..040) | nonce       | uint32  | 4     | Amount of sent messages        |
/// | [040..045) | blockNumber | uint40  | 5     | Block of last sent message     |
